      • getReportResult

        public final java.lang.String getReportResult(ReportFormParameters formParams)
        Provides a report preview.
        The JSON object holds information regarding:
        groupingOption
        - the timeframe by which to group funding data in the report
        add_columns
        - a list of columns names to be added to the report configuration
        add_hierarchies
        - a list of hierarchies to be added to the report configuration
        add_measures
        - a list of measures to be added to the report configuration
        filters
        - Report filters
        settings
        - Report settings



        Sample Input:

         {
  "groupingOption": "A",
  "add_columns": ["Activity Id",
  "Project Title",
  "Donor Agency",
  "Status",
  "AMP ID"],
  "add_hierarchies": ["Project Title"],
  "add_measures": ["Actual Commitments"],
  "filters": {
      "date": {
          "start": "2010-01-01",
          "end": "2015-12-31"
      }
  },
  "settings": {
      "funding-type": ["Actual Commitments",
      "Actual Disbursements"],
      "currency-code": "USD",
      "calendar-id": "123",
      "year-range": {
          "from": "2012",
          "to": "2014"
      }
  }
 }

        Sample Output:

       AMP ID
        #ni#column -> AMP ID        		
       Totals

        Returns:
        a HTML with the report preview
